<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Email Verification - WorkSync</title>
<style>
    body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
    }
    .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 20px auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #fff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .header img {
        max-width: 150px;
    }
    .content {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .footer {
        text-align: center;
    }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="header">
        <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/kMzLdbKm/Asset-1gg.png" width="60px" height="53px" alt="WorkSync Logo">
        <h3>WorkSync</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Dear User,</p>
        <p>Thank you for signing up with WorkSync! Please click the button below to verify your email address:</p>
        <p><a href="{{ signedUrl|raw }}" style="background-color: #5D87FF; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px;">Verify Email Address</a></p>
        <p>This link will expire in {{ expiresAtMessageKey|trans(expiresAtMessageData, 'VerifyEmailBundle') }}.</p>
        <p>If you did not sign up for WorkSync, please disregard this email.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact our support team at support@worksync.com.</p>
        <p>Thank you for choosing WorkSync!</p>
        <p>Best regards,<br>The WorkSync Team</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
